:: mod_websync ::

What is it ?
------------

A simple Apache 2 module for syncing web content between web servers.

The Latest Version
------------------

Details of the latest version can always be found on GitHub, under the
mod_websync project page: https://github.com/DougBridgens/mod_websync/.

Documentation
-------------

Please see the file called mod_websync.README

Installation
------------

Please see the file called INSTALL.

